              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-amber-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-amber-600 text-lg">üèîÔ∏è</span>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <span class="font-medium text-gray-900 group-hover:text-primary-600">Santiago</span>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Affordable prices, excellent quality of life</p>
              </div>
