        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-800 mb-2">No Restrictions for Foreign Buyers</h3>
            <p class="text-green-700">
              Foreigners can purchase property in {pais} with the exact same rights as Dominican nationals.
              You do not need residency or a special visa to buy. All you need is a valid passport, and our verified agents
